Skim milk powder and whey protein are good sources of calcium and protein respectively while fructose can contribute excess sugar intake if consumed in large amounts. Soy lecithin is a naturally occurring substance found in soya beans that may have potential health benefits but more research needs to be done on its long-term effects.
